You can use Lombok&#39;s @EqualsAndHashCode would be the fastest option.

Example and documentation can be found here: https://projectlombok.org/features/EqualsAndHashCode

If you create a new method in your class:

```
@EqualsAndHashCode(onlyExplicitlyIncluded = true)
class PersonKey {
  private String personUID;
  private String ssnUID;
  private String countryCode;

  ...

  @EqualsAndHashCode.Include
  public String uidOrSsn() {
     return personUID != null ? personUID : ssnUID;
  }

}

```

This way you&#39;re telling Lombok to only create the equals and hashCode for the `uidOrSsn()` method declared. Whichever the non-null value of personUID or ssnUID, then it will be generated.

