Your project setup seems to be broken. You are mixing artefacts from .m2 maven repository with an explicit SDK reference. See 17.0.2 vs 17.0.1.

In addition to the incorrect mixed Java version.  You are using the wrong version of jfoenix.  

[Read the jfoenix documentation](https://github.com/sshahine/JFoenix#maven)

Java 9+ needs a 9.x version of the library, not an 8.x version.

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;com.jfoenix&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;jfoenix&lt;/artifactId&gt;
